{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2020/05/23/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"SetValue.NET","author":"Raúl Fernández de Córdoba"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8e2664a2-9085-53cd-ae36-c558025f29bb","excerpt":"Hace poco se ha incluido una novedad en el registro de aplicaciones de Azure Active Directory. Azure siempre está incorporando alguna novedad, y ésta no podría…","html":"<p>Hace poco se ha incluido una novedad en el registro de aplicaciones de <strong>Azure Active Directory</strong>. Azure siempre está incorporando alguna novedad, y ésta no podría ser más útil.</p>\n<p>Tal y cómo se autodefine, su objetivo es ayudar a construir integraciones de alta calidad y seguras. Te muestra cuáles son las <em>best practices</em> y recomendaciones para ayudar a evitar descuidos habituales cuando nos integramos con la <strong>Microsoft Identity Platform</strong>.</p>\n<h2>App Registration</h2>\n<p>En la configuración del Azure Active Directory, en el apartado de <a href=\"https://portal.azure.com/#blade/Microsoft_AAD_IAM/ActiveDirectoryMenuBlade/RegisteredApps\" target=\"_blank\">App Registrations</a>, podemos seleccionar una aplicación que conozcamos cómo está configurada, y accedemos a su información del registro.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f834a1edb1f1188966172f671f384fcd/0f98f/AppRegistration-Overview.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"App Registration\"\n        title=\"App Registration\"\n        src=\"/static/f834a1edb1f1188966172f671f384fcd/ec7ce/AppRegistration-Overview.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f834a1edb1f1188966172f671f384fcd/3f316/AppRegistration-Overview.jpg 243w,\n/static/f834a1edb1f1188966172f671f384fcd/0d3a1/AppRegistration-Overview.jpg 485w,\n/static/f834a1edb1f1188966172f671f384fcd/ec7ce/AppRegistration-Overview.jpg 970w,\n/static/f834a1edb1f1188966172f671f384fcd/8010b/AppRegistration-Overview.jpg 1455w,\n/static/f834a1edb1f1188966172f671f384fcd/0f98f/AppRegistration-Overview.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Integration Assistant</h2>\n<p>En el menú lateral, encontramos un blade llamado <strong>Integration Assistant (preview)</strong>. Al acceder a él por primera vez, aparece un check list con el tipo de aplicación.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ddf1921d1d7230dc032e87a08846fd64/0f98f/AppRegistration-IAssistant.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant\"\n        src=\"/static/ddf1921d1d7230dc032e87a08846fd64/ec7ce/AppRegistration-IAssistant.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ddf1921d1d7230dc032e87a08846fd64/3f316/AppRegistration-IAssistant.jpg 243w,\n/static/ddf1921d1d7230dc032e87a08846fd64/0d3a1/AppRegistration-IAssistant.jpg 485w,\n/static/ddf1921d1d7230dc032e87a08846fd64/ec7ce/AppRegistration-IAssistant.jpg 970w,\n/static/ddf1921d1d7230dc032e87a08846fd64/8010b/AppRegistration-IAssistant.jpg 1455w,\n/static/ddf1921d1d7230dc032e87a08846fd64/0f98f/AppRegistration-IAssistant.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Una vez definido el tipo de aplicación que es, se evalúa y muestra el resumen de acciones verificadas.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c19cd058a21b05ef3fe854f8c9e0228b/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Summary\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Summary\"\n        src=\"/static/c19cd058a21b05ef3fe854f8c9e0228b/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c19cd058a21b05ef3fe854f8c9e0228b/3f316/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.jpg 243w,\n/static/c19cd058a21b05ef3fe854f8c9e0228b/0d3a1/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.jpg 485w,\n/static/c19cd058a21b05ef3fe854f8c9e0228b/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.jpg 970w,\n/static/c19cd058a21b05ef3fe854f8c9e0228b/8010b/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.jpg 1455w,\n/static/c19cd058a21b05ef3fe854f8c9e0228b/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Summary.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>El resumen nos indica que no hay configurada una URL a la que redirigirse cuando se completa el login, lógico porque en concreto este registro está en blanco, no se ha configurado nada. Por otro lado, nos indica que si vamos a utilizar el flujo de autenticación implícito, debemos habilitar los ID Tokens. Y si queremos configurar un sign-out, debemos configurar también una URL de Logout.</p>\n<h3>Develop</h3>\n<p>En la pestaña de Desarrollo, está información básica,  y recomendaciones de implementación y de Experiencia de Usuario.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6b87a63a4f1bb3249cc81274085b8434/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Develop\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Develop\"\n        src=\"/static/6b87a63a4f1bb3249cc81274085b8434/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6b87a63a4f1bb3249cc81274085b8434/3f316/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.jpg 243w,\n/static/6b87a63a4f1bb3249cc81274085b8434/0d3a1/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.jpg 485w,\n/static/6b87a63a4f1bb3249cc81274085b8434/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.jpg 970w,\n/static/6b87a63a4f1bb3249cc81274085b8434/8010b/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.jpg 1455w,\n/static/6b87a63a4f1bb3249cc81274085b8434/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Develop.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Estas recomendaciones nos dan acceso a artículos de la MSDN.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8f3e08218497725c6f72c2d95ae0dbc4/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Develop Recommendations\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Develop Recommendations\"\n        src=\"/static/8f3e08218497725c6f72c2d95ae0dbc4/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8f3e08218497725c6f72c2d95ae0dbc4/3f316/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.jpg 243w,\n/static/8f3e08218497725c6f72c2d95ae0dbc4/0d3a1/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.jpg 485w,\n/static/8f3e08218497725c6f72c2d95ae0dbc4/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.jpg 970w,\n/static/8f3e08218497725c6f72c2d95ae0dbc4/8010b/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.jpg 1455w,\n/static/8f3e08218497725c6f72c2d95ae0dbc4/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Develop-Recommendation.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Test</h3>\n<p>En la pestaña de Test, se incluyen otras recomendaciones relacionadas con el Testing y con la Experiencia de Usuario. Algunas de estas últimas también recomendadas en el apartado de <strong>Develop</strong>.</p>\n<p>Sugerencias como que verifiques las políticas de Acceso Condicional por si pueden impedir a los usuarios utilizar la aplicación, resultan obvias, pero que no siempre reparamos en validarlo.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9beefbe74221f48dbd3a68e700b7d824/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Test.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Test\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Test\"\n        src=\"/static/9beefbe74221f48dbd3a68e700b7d824/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Test.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9beefbe74221f48dbd3a68e700b7d824/3f316/IntegrationAssistant-Test.jpg 243w,\n/static/9beefbe74221f48dbd3a68e700b7d824/0d3a1/IntegrationAssistant-Test.jpg 485w,\n/static/9beefbe74221f48dbd3a68e700b7d824/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Test.jpg 970w,\n/static/9beefbe74221f48dbd3a68e700b7d824/8010b/IntegrationAssistant-Test.jpg 1455w,\n/static/9beefbe74221f48dbd3a68e700b7d824/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Test.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Release</h3>\n<p>El apartado de Release, nos muestra cuatro apartados:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Ownership</strong>. Nos recomienda agregar la información de contacto y que validemos si está realmente actualizada.</li>\n<li><strong>Branding</strong>. Incluir la información de marca con el logo y el nombre que mejor represente a tu compañía o producto, y por supuesto asegurarte de que no afecta a ninguna marca registrada.</li>\n<li><strong>Security</strong>. Minimizar y monitorizar manualmente la lista de propietarios de la aplicación o hacer rotados de credenciales.</li>\n<li><strong>End user experience</strong>. Incluir los certificados correspondientes si se está desarrollando una aplicación para Microsoft 365.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/76330aa3834ea2e739e72d86f2c97f74/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Release.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Release\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Release\"\n        src=\"/static/76330aa3834ea2e739e72d86f2c97f74/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Release.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/76330aa3834ea2e739e72d86f2c97f74/3f316/IntegrationAssistant-Release.jpg 243w,\n/static/76330aa3834ea2e739e72d86f2c97f74/0d3a1/IntegrationAssistant-Release.jpg 485w,\n/static/76330aa3834ea2e739e72d86f2c97f74/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Release.jpg 970w,\n/static/76330aa3834ea2e739e72d86f2c97f74/8010b/IntegrationAssistant-Release.jpg 1455w,\n/static/76330aa3834ea2e739e72d86f2c97f74/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Release.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Monitor</h3>\n<p>El último apartado, encontramos recomendaciones de monitorización. Algunas ya incluidas en otros apartados, y otras orientadas al ciclo de vida de una aplicación.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 970px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e5d562f87ddcc4a7a0fe250070e5d482/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.32098765432099%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Integration Assistant - Monitor\"\n        title=\"Integration Assistant - Monitor\"\n        src=\"/static/e5d562f87ddcc4a7a0fe250070e5d482/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e5d562f87ddcc4a7a0fe250070e5d482/3f316/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.jpg 243w,\n/static/e5d562f87ddcc4a7a0fe250070e5d482/0d3a1/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.jpg 485w,\n/static/e5d562f87ddcc4a7a0fe250070e5d482/ec7ce/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.jpg 970w,\n/static/e5d562f87ddcc4a7a0fe250070e5d482/8010b/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.jpg 1455w,\n/static/e5d562f87ddcc4a7a0fe250070e5d482/0f98f/IntegrationAssistant-Monitor.jpg 1920w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Integration Assistant Azure AD","date":"2020, May 23","description":"Azure Active Directory tiene una novedad en el registro de aplicaciones para facilitar la configuración de un registro de aplicación.","tags":["Azure","Azure AD","Microsoft Identity Platform"],"img":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.941544885177453,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","sizes":"(max-width: 1940px) 100vw, 1940px","src":"/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/6b48d/Preview.jpg","srcSet":"/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/2f037/Preview.jpg 930w,\n/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/23f4e/Preview.jpg 1860w,\n/static/179817ecd26e6c802e35ccd5032bed6f/6b48d/Preview.jpg 1940w"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2020/05/23/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/05/17/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"GatsbyJS en GitHub Pages con Azure DevOps","tags":["Azure DevOps","GitHub Pages","GatsbyJS"],"img":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.941544885177453,"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","sizes":"(max-width: 1940px) 100vw, 1940px","src":"/static/3e0e25a8b98af55bd3d2e435e7fdfbaa/6b48d/DevOps%2BGitHub.jpg","srcSet":"/static/3e0e25a8b98af55bd3d2e435e7fdfbaa/2f037/DevOps%2BGitHub.jpg 930w,\n/static/3e0e25a8b98af55bd3d2e435e7fdfbaa/23f4e/DevOps%2BGitHub.jpg 1860w,\n/static/3e0e25a8b98af55bd3d2e435e7fdfbaa/6b48d/DevOps%2BGitHub.jpg 1940w"}}}}},"next":null}}}